tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ClimateChangeData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    city VARCHAR,
    temperature FLOAT,
    precipitation FLOAT,
    carbon_emissions FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Climate_Data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    year INT,
    month VARCHAR(20),
    temperature FLOAT,
    precipitation FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Research_Teams (
    team_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    team_name VARCHAR(50),
    team_lead VARCHAR(50),
    research_area VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE Projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(100),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    team_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE Publications (
    publication_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    publication_title VARCHAR(100),
    publication_date DATE,
    author VARCHAR(50),
    project_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE climate_data (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location VARCHAR,
  temperature FLOAT,
  humidity FLOAT,
  date DATE);

CREATE TABLE research_team (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  team_name VARCHAR,
  team_lead VARCHAR,
  research_area VARCHAR);

CREATE TABLE research_projects (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR,
  project_description TEXT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE publications (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  publication_title VARCHAR,
  authors TEXT,
  publication_date DATE,
  citation_count INT);

CREATE TABLE funding_sources (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  source_name VARCHAR,
  funding_amount FLOAT,
  funding_purpose TEXT,
  grant_date DATE);
